            password, and other account details.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Non-Personal Information:</strong> We may automatically collect certain non-personal information,
            such as IP address, browser type, device type, and the pages you visit on our Site.
            This information is used to help us maintain and improve the functionality of our Site.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Card: How We Use Your Information -->
