            identify usage trends, troubleshoot issues, and improve our Site’s design and user experience.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Customer Support:</strong> If you contact us with questions or concerns, we may use your
            personal information to respond effectively.
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Legal Compliance:</strong> Where required, we may use or disclose your personal information
            to comply with applicable laws, regulations, legal processes, or government requests.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
