          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Business Transfers:</strong> If we are involved in a merger, acquisition, asset sale,
            or other corporate transaction, your information may be transferred as part of that transaction
            subject to standard confidentiality arrangements.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
